Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.30,0:02:59.95,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}言語 嚥回腹中
Dialogue: 1,0:03:00.08,0:03:03.28,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}記憶 鎖在心裡
Dialogue: 1,0:03:03.40,0:03:08.18,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}如今只要 回應這振動就好
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.07,0:03:11.23,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}睜開心眼 Lock-on!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.82,0:03:13.98,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}你在呼喊 Push up!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:14.56,0:03:18.69,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這痛楚和灼熱便是答案!!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:19.38,0:03:22.00,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}-你還能繼續戰鬥-
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.15,0:03:24.60,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}這是幻聽嗎?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.60,0:03:30.32,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}意識 用意志來引導
Dialogue: 1,0:03:30.42,0:03:35.58,op_zh,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur1.5}{\fad(200,200)}謹記不要被吞入 那不見底的深淵
